==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*παραλύω / paraluō / par-al-oo'-o
*From [[παρά]] {{GG|3844}} and [[λύω]] {{GG|3089}}; to loosen beside, that is, relax (perfect passive participle paralyzed or enfeebled): 

===Adjective===
'''παραλύω'''

# [[feeble]], [[sick]] of the (taken with) palsy.

